self_exclude.subtitle: Ṣakoso taara jade apo ara ẹni
self_exclude.description: Iyakọ ara ẹni jẹ́ iṣẹ ti ara ẹni laaye lati ṣe iranlọwọ fun ara ẹni lati yakọ taara jade apo. Nigbati o forukọsilẹ pelu Rejista Iyakọ Ara Ẹni, awọn oniṣẹ ti o yẹ yoo ṣe akiyesi lati ṣe irinwọ lati di aladde nipa awọn iṣẹ wọn.

assessment.title: Ayẹwo Eewọ
assessment.subtitle: Gba idanwo gbigberi taara jade apo
assessment.description: Ayẹwo yii n ṣe iranlọwọ fun awa laaye lati loye awọn ero taara jade apo rẹ ati irun eewọ.
assessment.page_subtitle: Tẹkọ ara awọn iṣẹ taara jade apo rẹ
assessment.low_risk_interpretation: Ayẹwo rẹ ṣafihan iṣẹ taara jade apo ti o kere eewọ. Ṣẹtọjọ awọn iṣẹ ti o dara ati ṣakoso iṣẹ rẹ.
assessment.medium_risk_interpretation: Ayẹwo rẹ ṣafihan iṣẹ taara jade apo ti o ga ti nipa. Tẹkọ ju lo awọn idi ati tẹkọ awọn iṣẹ rẹ.
assessment.high_risk_interpretation: Ayẹwo rẹ ṣafihan iṣẹ taara jade apo ti o ga eewọ. Atilẹyin agbajumo ti o ṣe akiyesi.
assessment.severe_risk_interpretation: Ayẹwo rẹ ṣafihan iṣẹ taara jade apo ti o ba nilo agbajumo. Atilẹyin agbajumo ti o gbe ni agbara ti o ṣe akiyesi.
assessment.next_step_1: Tẹkọ awọn ero taara jade apo rẹ ati ṣe awọn idin
assessment.next_step_2: Tẹkọ sọrọ pelu alabawe tabi oluwàlòpó
assessment.next_step_3: Gba ayẹwo tuntun ninu ọjọ 30 lati ṣakoso iluwo

help.title: Iranlọwọ ati Atilẹyin
help.subtitle: Gba iranlọwọ ati ohun elo
help.how_it_works: Bawo Ni Iyakọ Ara Ẹni Se Ṣiṣẹ
help.what_is_self_exclusion_answer: Iyakọ ara ẹni jẹ́ iṣẹ ti o gba ẹ laaye lati beere lati yakọ ara ẹni kuro ninu gbogbo awọn oniṣẹ ti o ni iṣẹ fun akoko ti o yan. Lakoko yii, awọn oniṣẹ ni iṣẹ to ṣẹto lati yẹda ẹ kuro ninu awọn iṣẹ wọn.
help.can_cancel_early: Ṣe o le fagile iyakọ ara ẹni mi kọjá?
help.can_cancel_early_answer: Rara, iyakọ ara ẹni jẹ́ ipin ati ko le fagile lakoko yii. Eyi jẹ́ dandan lati ṣe ifigagbọkun. Nipa awọn ọran pataki laara nikan ni a le ṣe akiyesi fun gbigbe kọjá - ba atolẹyin fun alaye.
help.will_carry_over: Ṣe iyakọ ara ẹni mi yoo gba oniṣẹ oniṣẹ?
help.will_carry_over_answer: Bẹ́ẹ̀ ni! Iyakọ ara ẹni rẹ jẹ́ forukọsilẹ ninu akosọ ìbílẹ̀ ati gbogbo awọn oniṣẹ ti o ni iṣẹ gbọdọ ṣayẹwo akosọ yii nigbati o ba gbiyanju lati jin awọn iṣẹ wọn.
help.update_profile: Bawo ni mo ṣe gbe alaye profaili mi?
help.update_profile_answer: O le gbe profaili rẹ nipa lilo Awọn Iyikalọ Akạ ninu ibadandun rẹ. O le ṣatunṣe alaye ṣokan, awọn iṣedede, ati awọn alaye akạ miiran.
help.verify_identity: Bawo ni mo ṣe jẹrìsí ẹni mi?
help.verify_identity_answer: O le jẹ gbẹ jẹrìsí ID nipa Awọn Iyikalọ Akạ. Kin ọna iyalẹnu ti a fun nipa ilu ati a yoo jẹrìsí ni igba 24-48.
help.enable_2fa: Bawo ni mo ṣe jẹ ihò ibalopọ-aláwo?
help.enable_2fa_answer: Lọ si Awọn Iyikalọ Ifigagbọkun ati jẹ ihò 2FA. Iwọ yoo gba awọn koodu nipa SMS tabi oniṣẹ ọkọọkan fun ifigagbọkun akạ ti o ga.
help.account_compromised: Kini mo ṣe ti akạ mi ba ti pajade?
help.account_compromised_answer: Ṣatunṣe ọrọ isilẹ rẹ laṣegọ ati jẹ ihò 2FA ti ko ba ṭijẹ. Ti o ba ṣusurú ibadandun ti a ko ṛohun, ba atolẹyin laṣegọ pelu alaye akạ rẹ.
help.available_assessments: Awọn ayẹwo taara jade apo melo ni o si?
help.available_assessments_answer: A nifẹrẹ ayẹwo mẹta ti o ni iṣẹ: LIEBET (gbigberi fun pẹpẹ), PGSI (lapapọ), ati DSM-5 (alaye ìmọ́). Awọn wọnyii ṣe iranlọwọ lati ṣe ayẹwo irun eewọ taara jade apo rẹ.
